<p>Unfortunately, I found that the JS I used may conflict with Bootstrap JS. I can only click the link but the page didnâ€™t go to the new link address. In the end I used HTML within php function to switch class from last â€œ&lt;<strong>li</strong>&gt;â€ to current â€œ&lt;<strong>li</strong>&gt;â€.</p>

